data.text:
This ranking shows the most popular RuPaul's Drag Race queens according to their total number of Likes on Facebook. There are a number of other factors that would need to be incorporated to determine actual 'popularity', but this list gives us a rough idea. Each ranking is linked to the queen's Facebook fan page so Like all your favorites and support your queens!
